{"TopicId":208538,"ForumId":24,"TopicTitle":"Hi - looking forward to learning how to get the most from KSP - got two initial questions","CreatedByName":"besp09","CreatedById":221771,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-10T18:55:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"besp09","CreatedById":221771,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-10T18:55:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJumped straight into the Training scenarios - luckily already seen a post on this section of the forum saying some of the tutorials are broken. Spent a long time looking for parts not showing in parts list.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.0 Is it worth me installing the mod - or I am best using youtube and starting a career?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2.0 Is the only way to install mods via curseforge (assume this is a 3rd party site) or can they be added via steam?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-10T19:00:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224143348\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208538\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221654887315\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221771\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022besp09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, besp09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2.0 Is the only way to install mods via curseforge (assume this is a 3rd party site) or can they be added via steam?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are other ways:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022187982\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5706733485\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/182950-tutorial-how-to-install-mods-manually-ckan/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-10T19:05:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would advise new players to get used to the stock game before they start modifying it. This avoids confusion about whether issues they encounter are stock features, bugs, or effects of the mods.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut whatever your choice, welcome to the forum. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"besp09","CreatedById":221771,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-11T12:40:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224143350\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208538\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221654887614\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156657\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HebaruSan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, HebaruSan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are other ways:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022187982\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed707859908\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspac